<h4><span lang=EN-US>7.2.1.5 </span><span style='font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
Cambria;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:
major-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Cambria;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-latin'>实地查验法</span>
</h4>

<p style='text-indent:24.0pt'>实地查验法主要针对业务层面控制，通过对企业财产进行盘点、清查，以及针对业务流程中的各个控制环节进行现场查验等方式，进行控制测试。如现场查验存货出、入库环节。
</p>

<h4><span lang=EN-US>7.2.1.6 </span><span style='font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
Cambria;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:
major-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Cambria;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-latin'>专题讨论法</span>
</h4>

<p style='text-indent:24.0pt'>专题讨论法是指集中与业务流程有关的专业人员就内部控制执行情况或控制缺陷进行分析，既可以是控制评价的手段，也是形成缺陷整改方案的途径。比如，对于同时涉及企业多个业务部门的控制缺陷，由内部控制管理部门组织召开专题讨论会议，综合各方面意见，研究确定整改方案。<span
style='font-size:5.5pt;font-family:"Tahoma","sans-serif"'> </span></p>

<h3><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:"Arial","sans-serif"'>7.2.2 </span>内部控制评价程序<span
style='font-size:5.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:"Tahoma","sans-serif"'> </span></h3>

<p style='text-indent:24.0pt'><i><span lang=EN-US style='color:red'>[</span><span
style='color:red'>描述内控评价程序<span lang=EN-US>]</span></span></i><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:5.5pt;font-family:"Tahoma","sans-serif"'> </span></p>

<p style='text-indent:24.0pt'><span style='color:black'>内部控制评价程序主要可分为三个阶段，分别为准备阶段、自评价阶段、及整改报告阶段。具体如下：</span><span
style='font-size:5.5pt;font-family:"Tahoma","sans-serif"'> </span></p>

<h4><span lang=EN-US>7.2.2.1</span><span style='font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
Cambria;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:
major-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Cambria;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-latin'>流程图</span></h4>

<h4><i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'><span lang=EN-US><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape
